      • loadEvaluatorImpl

        public static EvalInterface loadEvaluatorImpl(String matchCode,
                                              String codedData,
                                              String molName)
                                       throws ParameterException
        Load the specific class of EvaluatorImpl according to matchCode.
        Parameters:
        matchCode - short code unique to an evaluator type
        codedData - slash-separated series of short strings and numbers, such as "Y>/5", that an evaluator uses to evaluate a response
        molName - name of molecule (if any) that evaluator compares to the response
        Returns:
        instance of a class for evaluating a response
        Throws:
        ParameterException - if the coded data is malformed
